      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MISS WILDCAT (8) has been in the money at her last three runs, all over today's journey. Cause wasn't helped when she jumped awkwardly at the Gold Coast last start but the final stages were strong. Brings superior form to this race and it will be a big surprise if she doesn't break through today. COMMEDIA (7) has been well back at both runs this prep and been left with far too much to do. Back a little in distance but the addition of blinkers may add that bit of spark required. YES KISS (6) is back from a year off the scene and is now in a new stable. Yet to place in 12 runs but in a race without depth a top three finish is achievable. AERIAL ARTIST (2) resumes. Has shown nothing in two runs to date but a recent gelding operation may turn things around. The others cannot win on performances to date.",
